  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he dictates something to the secretary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She typed on a typewriter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was hand write typer, no electric typer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She will type very fast and gave it to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he read it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, this what you wanted?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I says, this is perfect. .",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And gave it to me and naturally put the signature, put the German swastika big stamp, which was-- I said, oh, this is what I wanted.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And gave it to me and said, and I don't want to see you ever again here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I put my feet like a German soldier together, salute him, and said, no, you will never see me again, and I walk out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And walk out and went to the place where he was parking the in a backyard of some house someplace and-- and I said we can go back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So went back and came to the priest and gave him the document.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Oh, this is like a from heaven and Jesus must be with me, he said, because I got something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't make any comment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Never I made any comments.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he said, what do we do with this now?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You ask for that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So he said he really didn't know because he was very, very crude man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was-- he didn't very well-educated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know what he got education, where he was born, but from his speech, you could tell also that [INAUDIBLE] men.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we went-- so I told him again we had to go Lithuanian civilian the voivodeship and present this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he didn't know Lithuanian, and asked me if I would do-- represent him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I went next day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And came to the fellow and show it to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
